RBT_PREPA_RGT-Integration/I1-W_RBT_PREPA_RGT-Prepare/Drop of pre-integration table/SQL_TRANSACTION_TYPE" type="String" vName="SQL_TRANSACTION_TYPE" value="AUTOCOMMIT"/></step><step actionName="com_maj_remboursement/330 DB Prepa RET_REGLEMENT_RBT(montant origine)/I1-W_RBT_PREPA_RGT-Integration/I1-W_RBT_PREPA_RGT-Prepare/Analyze of pre-integration table (DBMS_STATS.GATHER_TABLE_STATS method)" id="9259133665686f5406185a84473a381d" isBeginAction="false" nbCycles="-1" restartPoint="default" technology="com.indy.engine.actionCodes.JdbcActionCodeI" toleratedError="true" type="Code"><![CDATA[BEGIN 
